title: BlazBlue Gallery Artwork Rebel 1
description:
The Wheel of Fate is Turning!

This is the first round of gallery pictures from BlazBlue.  I took pictures of my 32' LCD TV using a 7.2 MP digital camera.  I took over 200 pictures and only these 26 came out looking halfway decent.  I cropped them and adjusted colors, contrast, brightness, etc. until I thought they were acceptable.  Unfortunately there is still some loss of quality, but I did my best.  They are still in very high resolution, so they are about 650 KB-1 MB each.  

This is only the first round of pics.  I plan on going back through and trying to get good pics of all the ones I missed.  I took all these at night, so I think if I try again during the day I will get different results.  Enjoy, and please comment.
